review.comments:
barbara was quick to respond for all our messages and very helpfull and nice. the neighbourhood is great and the appartment is huge, comfortable and look exactly the as the pictures.
before you book keep in mind that this is a quiet neighbourhood so if you want to party in the house this is not the place for you, otherwise I highly recommend this appartment.
